org.nd4j.linalg.jcublas.ops.executioner

Class CudaExecutioner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nd4j.linalg.api.ops.executioner.DefaultOpExecutioner
      • org.nd4j.linalg.jcublas.ops.executioner.CudaExecutioner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OpExecutioner
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CudaGridExecutioner

    public class CudaExecutioner
extends DefaultOpExecutioner
    JCuda executioner.

    Runs ops directly on the gpu If requested Op doesn't exist within GPU context, DefaultOpExecutioner will be used, with arrays/buffers updated after that.
